sour brandsour businessescareersitt total rewardssearch open positionspurpose and principlescandidate faqinclusion  diversityeverifyaccessibilitycitizenshipgovernance and ethicsemployees and workplaceenvironmentcommunity involvementproduct stewardshipcontactinvestor contactsshareholder servicesbrand contacts our products showcasing a selection of our highly engineered solutions   our goulds pumps brand xhd extra heavy duty lined slurry pump incorporates the latest technology to meet customers’ most important needs including high efficiency and extended wear life along with maximum reliability and ease of maintenance the result of more than  years of slurry pump experience this product is designed for the toughest applications and was named a breakthrough product of the year by processing magazine our enidine brand viscous dampers are hydraulic devices that help protect customers’ structure and systems from unwanted shock and vibration due to earthquakes or other seismic events these versatile devices are used on bridges highrise buildings stadiums and city centers custom solutions have also been developed for power and utility substations power plants oil and gas offshore platforms and refinery and storage facilities with coming changes in the use of wireless devices airline operators are preparing to offer services allowing passengers wireless connectivity inflight our customized rack and panel connectors are based on a highly successful connector line used in commercial aircraft for highspeed connectivity in flight these connectors help facilitate the wireless connectivity video data and power that service most passenger applications as well as plane sensors and security video our innovative koni frequency selective damping technology is just one reason we are a leading manufacturer of highperformance shock absorbers this technology helps provide appropriate damping forces across a range of speed and input frequencies helping reduce equipment wear while improving safety and performance it’s a clear reflect ion of our goal of meeting the diverse demands of our automotive customers with sophisticated solutions that combine both comfort and roadholding  our pureflo high purity diaphragm valves address the needs of the pharmaceutical bioprocessing and food and beverage industries for highquality welded and quick disconnect process systems pureflo assemblies and fabrications have been developed primarily to minimize contact surfaces and hold up volume the pureflo product line offers a complete line of cast forged and wrought bodies to meet the needs and requirements of customers’ process application our highperformance highquality automotive brake pads primarily serve the highend of the transportation industry with a reputation for quality products and a focus on new product development and operational excellence we apply innovative research in new friction materials and productive technologies to manufacture a range of brake pads that meet the demands of a variety of end customers and automotive platforms around the world media  leaders in stem view the publication the history of itt download the itt history book brt sustainability report learn how itt is delivering shared success annual report itts  annual report to shareholders our products  itt inc search for  menu home about history leadership board of directors purpose and principles suppliers news releases itt signature stories media library publications investors at a glance investor news presentations earnings nongaap reconciliations financial statements shareholder services governance expertise our markets energy our markets transportation our markets industrial our products our brands our businesses careers itt total rewards search open positions purpose and principles candidate faq inclusion  diversity everify accessibility citizenship governance and ethics employees and workplace environment community involvement product stewardship contact investor contacts sharehol