ery service and support contact us today to see how our products can benefit your specific equipment application needs or alternatively you may find one of our many representatives to help you meet your product requirements news itt to release secondquarter results on aug  monday  jul  more news come visit us why it pays to understand shock and vibration throughout the manufacturing industry shock and vibration damages equipment slows production and leads to product quality defects this recorded presentation will characterize the most prevalent forms of shock and vibration to help attendees select the management and control solutions best suited to their applications click here to register today want to learn more please submit our online inquiry form to learn more about our industrial products and services industrial learn more explore itt enidine general industrial products and services aviation learn more view the latest innovations in aviation products and services defense learn more protecting our troops and providing the latest technologies seismic learn more protecting valuable assets and structures from seismic events global representatives search now find the sales representative nearest to you itt factbook learn more itt has a long standing reputation of providing diversified solutions to global markets with a diverse product portfolio featured solutions learn more our latest shock absorber product offerings with technical data and dimensional information for your specific application requirements we are a proud member of the national fluid power association learn more itt products  glx scale models inc itt products  glx scale models inc contact us  no items itt products animate your scene with sound itt products makes it easy… good selection of sounds modules from innovative train technologies for your model railroading layout or diorama electrical hook up can be done to a variety of power sources  pre recorded original sound clips are up to  seconds in l